            "description": "<article class=\"post-body\" data-v-1d7d601f=\"\">\n<h3 style=\"text-indent: 0em; text-align: left;\">\n<span style=\"font-family: sans-serif;\">今日看点</span>\n</h3>\n<ul class=\"list-paddingleft-2\" style=\"list-style-type: decimal;\">\n<li>\n<p style=\"text-indent: 0em; text-align: left;\">\n<a href=\"https://data.iyiou.com/intelligence/details/b8a33434414cdebaec85c845f54e42d6?source=iyiou.dgs\" target=\"_blank\"><strong style=\"font-size: 18px;\">京东申请注册京东医美商标</strong></a><br/>\n</p>\n<p style=\"text-indent: 0em; text-align: left;display: block;\">\n</p>\n</li>\n<li>\n<p style=\"text-indent: 0em; text-align: left;\">\n<a href=\"https://data.iyiou.com/intelligence/details/ed90c34a7312680613687c6cc9e389de?source=iyiou.dgs\" target=\"_blank\"><strong style=\"font-size: 18px;\">华为引望申请时空数字底盘引擎商标</strong></a><br/>\n</p>\n<p style=\"text-indent: 0em; text-align: left;display: block;\">\n</p>\n</li>\n</ul>\n<p style=\"margin-top:0pt; margin-bottom:0pt; font-size:11pt\">\n<br/>\n</p>\n<h3 style=\"text-indent: 0em; text-align: left;\">\n        今日情报（2家2条）\n    </h3>\n<ul class=\"list-paddingleft-2\" style=\"list-style-type: disc;\">\n<li>\n<p style=\"text-indent: 0em; text-align: left;\">\n<span style=\"font-size: 18px;\"><strong>\n<a href=\"https://data.iyiou.com/company/details/3abac56002850c725f953ec5009b7172/profile?source=iyiou.dgs\" target=\"_blank\">京东</a>\n</strong></span>\n</p>\n</li>\n</ul>\n<p style=\"text-indent: 0em; text-align: left;\">\n<a href=\"https://data.iyiou.com/intelligence/details/b8a33434414cdebaec85c845f54e42d6?source=iyiou.dgs\" target=\"_blank\">京东申请注册京东医美商标</a>\n</p>\n<ul class=\"list-paddingleft-2\" style=\"list-style-type: disc;\">\n<li>\n<p style=\"text-indent: 0em; text-align: left;\">\n<span style=\"font-size: 18px;\"><strong>\n<a href=\"https://data.iyiou.com/company/details/de28ed3891949e2212e11541f3c950a5/profile?source=iyiou.dgs\" target=\"_blank\">华为</a>\n</strong></span>\n</p>\n</li>\n</ul>\n<p style=\"text-i